Title: Paper Requisition (search)
Text: Sneak around Petrolton City Hall to search through desks for a secret document
CompleteText:
I've found an envelope marked "CONFIDENTIAL", though some of the labels have something to do with farming... who wants documents about agriculture this badly?
I'll need to bring this to the Ghetto. It must be that dingy looking place on the northern side of Petrolton, but I'll have to search for whoever looks ready for a suspicious delivery.
